{"id": 1483, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今你评价事物，都在心里设置了哪些及格线？", "description": "别说业界良心了，咱能先踏实过六十分吗？（题图来自：Timo Kuilder）", "record_count": 17765, "comment_count": 26, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201702071515518DKVlkyEXRxzGdtu.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-02-07T17:00:43Z", "questions": [{"id": 1851, "title": "现如今你评价事物，都在心里设置了哪些及格线？", "content": "现如今你评价事物，都在心里设了哪些及格线？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 163344, "content": "对喜剧的要求是“不胳肢人”（不硬让人笑）", "image": "img/option/option/20170207160711Kvy23uJmdNqIWUlb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 163347, "content": "对安利的要求是“感谢推荐，我的钱包又瘦了”", "image": "img/option/option/2017020716093159SGsi3HaJtp01R8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 163350, "content": "对快递的要求是“八角尖尖”，不要被压得屎一样", "image": "img/option/option/20170207161424sIRazvV40rkCgOnJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 163352, "content": "网购护肤品的要求是“距离保质期至少有小半年”", "image": "img/option/option/20170207162116CtI2lJMHw4paiE6L.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 163354, "content": "对演员的要求是“好好念台词别数数，以及不要抠像”", "image": "img/option/option/20170207162502Tn4YlXR0rPGf7F1m.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 163355, "content": "对知乎回答的要求是“不讲故事不放二维码”", "image": "img/option/option/20170207162624ApmFc3nCGoYVgKRP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 163358, "content": "对专车的要求…现在能不加价打到就可以满分了", "image": "img/option/option/20170207163443XW0qpGxwrRIjHmcC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 163357, "content": "对自拍的要求是……“别发”", "image": "img/option/option/20170207163154JioSvsUOphzAIBGc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}